# - Try to find the CascLib library
# Once done this will define
#
#  CASCLIB_FOUND - system has CascLib
#  CASCLIB_INCLUDE_DIR - the CASCLIB include directory
#  CASCLIB_LIBRARY - The CASCLIB library

